# Tool Gateway

- Default bind: `127.0.0.1` (`TOOL_GATEWAY_HOST`). Do not revert to `0.0.0.0` without explicit reason.
- HarmonyOS app uses a fixed gateway base URL (`http://127.0.0.1:8787` via `defaultToolGatewayUrl()`). Do not expose an editable gateway URL in the config UI; show it read-only in technical diagnostics only.
- Optional auth: set `TOOL_GATEWAY_API_KEY` in `.env.local`; clients send `Authorization: Bearer <key>` or `X-API-Key`.
- `/health` and `/mcp/tools` stay unauthenticated; `/api/aiphone/tool` and `/mcp/call` require auth when key is set.
- Tool streams emit `pendingA2ui` then result; client merges same `surfaceId` createSurface without clearing components.
- App does not keyword-route prompts. `callLocalModel` always sends one unified `SYSTEM_PROMPT`; tool calls happen only when model writes `/toolRequest` and `Index.callModelRequestedTool` reads it.
- Model thinking must stay on the active surface (`surface_model` after first model envelope). Do not bounce back to `surface_model_thinking` once `surface_model` exists.
- `A2uiSurfaceStore.createSurface` must preserve `/thoughts` when switching `surfaceId`; `showModelThinking` always writes to `store.getSurface().surfaceId`.
- UI reads thinking via page-level `persistedThinkingText` / `ThinkingPanel` (auto-expand while streaming; auto-collapse when `</think>` / `` is seen via `A2uiStreamMeta.thinkClosed`). Hide A2UI `ThinkingStream`/`ThinkingCard` in `RenderComponent`.
- Tool gateway calls must `store.seed(currentSurface)` so pending/result envelopes merge instead of flashing empty surfaces.
- `updateDataModel /thoughts` must not replace longer model thinking with shorter tool stub arrays.
- Train search (`train.search`): gateway returns up to `TRAIN_RESULT_LIMIT` (default 30) structured `/trains` rows with seat fields; filters G/D and optional `parseDepartAfter` from prompt (e.g. 晚上六点之后 → 18:00).
- Train quick actions use `A2uiAction.kind`: `client` (`client_show_more`, `client_sort_fastest`, `client_filter_available`) handled in `Index.sendAction` without model round-trip; `input` (`client_edit_query`) focuses the input dock. Do not reintroduce vague「换个时间/换个车站」prompt actions.
- Food search (`food.search`): `Index.callModelRequestedTool` sends the user's original prompt (not model-rewritten `/toolRequest.prompt`) so location text is preserved. Gateway resolves `地点附近的关键词` via Amap POI text search for landmark-like places (华为/基地/园区等), otherwise `/v3/geocode/geo` with `city`, then `/v3/place/around`; `AMAP_DEFAULT_LOCATION` is fallback only when both fail. `FoodChoices` ForEach keys must be stable (no `revision` suffix) to avoid duplicate rows during tool streaming.
